{"ja509:0.1":"Jataka ","ja509:0.2":"Visatinipata ","ja509:0.3":"Matangavagga ","ja509:0.4":"13. Hatthipalajataka ","ja509:1.1":"“Cirassam vata passama, ","ja509:1.2":"brahmanam devavanninam; ","ja509:1.3":"Mahajatam kharidharam, ","ja509:1.4":"pankadantam rajassiram. ","ja509:2.1":"Cirassam vata passama, ","ja509:2.2":"isim dhammagune ratam; ","ja509:2.3":"Kasayavatthavasanam, ","ja509:2.4":"vakaciram paticchadam. ","ja509:3.1":"Asanam udakam pajjam, ","ja509:3.2":"patiganhatu no bhavam; ","ja509:3.3":"Agghe bhavantam pucchama, ","ja509:3.4":"aggham kurutu no bhavam”. ","ja509:4.1":"“Adhicca vede pariyesa vittam, ","ja509:4.2":"Putte gahe tata patitthapetva; ","ja509:4.3":"Gandhe rase paccanubhuyya sabbam, ","ja509:4.4":"Arannam sadhu muni so pasattho”. ","ja509:5.1":"“Veda na sacca na ca vittalabho, ","ja509:5.2":"Na puttalabhena jaram vihanti; ","ja509:5.3":"Gandhe rase muccanamahu santo, ","ja509:5.4":"Sakammuna hoti phalupapatti”. ","ja509:6.1":"“Addha hi saccam vacanam tavetam, ","ja509:6.2":"Sakammuna hoti phalupapatti; ","ja509:6.3":"Jinna ca matapitaro tavime, ","ja509:6.4":"Passeyyum tam vassasatam arogam”. ","ja509:7.1":"“Yassassa sakkhi maranena raja, ","ja509:7.2":"Jaraya metti naravirasettha; ","ja509:7.3":"Yo capi janna na marissam kadaci, ","ja509:7.4":"Passeyyum tam vassasatam arogam. ","ja509:8.1":"Yathapi navam puriso dakamhi, ","ja509:8.2":"Ereti ce nam upaneti tiram; ","ja509:8.3":"Evampi byadhi satatam jara ca, ","ja509:8.4":"Upaneti maccam vasamantakassa”. ","ja509:9.1":"“Panko ca kama palipo ca kama, ","ja509:9.2":"Manohara duttara maccudheyya; ","ja509:9.3":"Etasmim panke palipe byasanna, ","ja509:9.4":"Hinattarupa na taranti param. ","ja509:10.1":"Ayam pure luddamakasi kammam, ","ja509:10.2":"Svayam gahito na hi mokkhito me; ","ja509:10.3":"Orundhiya nam parirakkhissami, ","ja509:10.4":"Mayam puna luddamakasi kammam”. ","ja509:11.1":"“Gavamva nattham puriso yatha vane, ","ja509:11.2":"Anvesati raja apassamano; ","ja509:11.3":"Evam nattho esukari mamattho, ","ja509:11.4":"Soham katham na gaveseyyam raja. ","ja509:12.1":"Hiyyoti hiyyati poso, ","ja509:12.2":"Pareti parihayati; ","ja509:12.3":"Anagatam netamatthiti natva, ","ja509:12.4":"Uppannachandam ko panudeyya dhiro”. ","ja509:13.1":"“Passami voham daharam kumarim, ","ja509:13.2":"Mattupamam ketakapupphanettam; ","ja509:13.3":"Abhuttabhoge pathame vayasmim, ","ja509:13.4":"Adaya maccu vajate kumarim. ","ja509:14.1":"Yuva sujato sumukho sudassano, ","ja509:14.2":"Samo kusumbhaparikinnamassu; ","ja509:14.3":"Hitvana kame patikacca geham, ","ja509:14.4":"Anujana mam pabbajissami deva”. ","ja509:15.1":"“Sakhahi rukkho labhate samannam, ","ja509:15.2":"Pahinasakham pana khanumahu; ","ja509:15.3":"Pahinaputtassa mamajja bhoti, ","ja509:15.4":"Vasetthi bhikkhacariyaya kalo”. ","ja509:16.1":"“Aghasmi koncava yatha himaccaye, ","ja509:16.2":"Katani jalani padaliya hamsa; ","ja509:16.3":"Gacchanti putta ca pati ca mayham, ","ja509:16.4":"Saham katham nanuvaje pajanam”. ","ja509:17.1":"“Ete bhutva vamitva ca, ","ja509:17.2":"pakkamanti vihangama; ","ja509:17.3":"Ye ca bhutvana vamimsu, ","ja509:17.4":"te me hatthattamagata. ","ja509:18.1":"Avami brahmano kame, ","ja509:18.2":"so tvam paccavamissasi; ","ja509:18.3":"Vantado puriso raja, ","ja509:18.4":"na so hoti pasamsiyo”. ","ja509:19.1":"“Panke ca posam palipe byasannam, ","ja509:19.2":"Bali yatha dubbalamuddhareyya; ","ja509:19.3":"Evampi mam tvam udatari bhoti, ","ja509:19.4":"Pancali gathahi subhasitahi”. ","ja509:20.1":"Idam vatva maharaja, ","ja509:20.2":"esukari disampati; ","ja509:20.3":"Rattham hitvana pabbaji, ","ja509:20.4":"nago chetvava bandhanam. ","ja509:21.1":"“Raja ca pabbajjamarocayittha, ","ja509:21.2":"Rattham pahaya naravirasettho; ","ja509:21.3":"Tuvampi no hohi yatheva raja, ","ja509:21.4":"Amhehi gutta anusasa rajjam”. ","ja509:22.1":"“Raja ca pabbajjamarocayittha, ","ja509:22.2":"Rattham pahaya naravirasettho; ","ja509:22.3":"Ahampi eka carissami loke, ","ja509:22.4":"Hitvana kamani manoramani. ","ja509:23.1":"Raja ca pabbajjamarocayittha, ","ja509:23.2":"Rattham pahaya naravirasettho; ","ja509:23.3":"Ahampi eka carissami loke, ","ja509:23.4":"Hitvana kamani yathodhikani. ","ja509:24.1":"Accenti kala tarayanti rattiyo, ","ja509:24.2":"Vayoguna anupubbam jahanti; ","ja509:24.3":"Ahampi eka carissami loke, ","ja509:24.4":"Hitvana kamani manoramani. ","ja509:25.1":"Accenti kala tarayanti rattiyo, ","ja509:25.2":"Vayoguna anupubbam jahanti; ","ja509:25.3":"Ahampi eka carissami loke, ","ja509:25.4":"Hitvana kamani yathodhikani. ","ja509:26.1":"Accenti kala tarayanti rattiyo, ","ja509:26.2":"Vayoguna anupubbam jahanti; ","ja509:26.3":"Ahampi eka carissami loke, ","ja509:26.4":"Sitibhuta sabbamaticca sangan”ti. ","ja509:27.1":"Hatthipalajatakam terasamam. "}